folder: Franklin Avenue & Hancock Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Franklin Avenue, at Hancock Street. View 1 is south toward Fulton Street, where the "El" is.

View 2 shows the Bedford Branch of the Brooklyn Public Library, facing Hancock street, and view 3 the Moose Lodge No. 14, adjoining the library.

P. L. Sperr

August 24, 1941
Views 1-3
